Teri Keane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teri_Keane 0 Teri Keane (born October 24, 1925) is an actress known for her work in the era of old-time radio. She was reported to have "appeared in more than 100 dramatic roles in radio and television." For a twelve-year period, from Oct 1963 to April 4, 1975, she played Martha Spears Marceau, the wife of police chief Bill Marceau on the CBS-TV daytime drama The Edge of Night.
